{"tid":1654033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊體育停播NBA不足一周恢復直播","createTime":"2019-10-14T11:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T16:28:02.000Z","uid":173952,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eaec7c5ce880922727b2fdb2c7249c3dfcfa2da7","tid":1654033,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"【口裡說不】騰訊體育停播NBA不足一周恢復直播<br />\n<br />\nNBA球隊火箭總經理莫雷表態支持香港反修例，引發風波後不足一星期，騰訊體育恢復直播NBA季前熱身賽。有網民揶揄騰訊只是「暫時愛國」，風聲一過就繼續賺錢。"},{"pid":"107b3214c1f06633820b4428418d55f2bd0b2010","tid":1654033,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:11:20.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】騰訊體育恢復部分NBA賽事直播。<br />\n<br />\n根據騰訊體育網頁資料，公司恢復部分NBA賽事直播，包括公牛對速龍等賽事，但本周稍後舉行的火箭賽事，則未有出現在直播清單上。<br />\n<br />\nNBA球隊火箭總經理莫雷早前發表支持香港的言論，引起內地不滿。騰訊體育曾發聲明，暫停NBA季前賽的轉播安排。"},{"pid":"271f7d77c2b1e4f29107a7b13447f7fbd2b5b840","tid":1654033,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"笑死人"},{"pid":"f9d188ab5230193e210fd8662e91e7fb6bb0abd9","tid":1654033,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"又話唔睇nba轉睇cba既 好柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b388906c532c45de0a63c61322d01c2efde9f5f7","tid":1654033,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a623dddc12efefe5ffdc88d6768dbc84b5ce78","tid":1654033,"uid":75449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"【國際NBA戰線】10月15修頓,掀動全球抗共<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651826</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n聽晚見"},{"pid":"786ac2158008680b6de20e36c76c95d4f41d660e","tid":1654033,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"小支支 <img src=\"/ass